dmca.title: Dynamic Resource Group DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.body:
1. The copyrighted work at issue is the images that appear on
https://picasaweb.google.com/Nenugnoje.2 and the linking pages.  Digital
scans of copyright work from Annie's Attic, House of White Birches, American
School of Needlework, and The Needlecraft Shop are presented within the
website.  

.         Miniature Tea Set [Annie's Attic]

.         Jolly Ol St. Nick [Annie's Attic]

.         Striped Vest [Annie's Attic]

.         Whimsical Pot Holders [Annie's Attic]

.         Old Time Crochet [House of White Birches]

.         Love That Bag [American School of Needlework]

 

2. Allegedly Infringing Postings
